lines.text: (FR is calculated using the CKD-EPI 2021 equation
which does not use a race-based adjustment
Total cholesterol and HDL C used
for risk assessment and to calculate non-HDL C.
HDL-C <1.30 mmol/L indicates risk for metabolic syndrome.
For additional LDL-C and non-HDL-C thresholds
assessment, refer to apoB or non-HDL-C
